              "free_text": [
                "",
                "One stack containing 14 foils of high-purity",
                "nat zirconium (25 micron, 99.99%) and 14 beam current",
                "monitoring natural copper foils (10 micron) from",
                "Goodfellow,England, was irradiated with 17 MeV, 100nA",
                "protons.",
                "The decay data of the investigated nuclei were taken",
                "from Nudat 2.5(2010)."
              ]
            }
